# ==============================================================================
# INTEGRATED SYSTEM RELIABILITY MAP & EFFECTIVE LOD RESOLUTION PIPELINE
# Effective LOD is max(INSTRUMENT_LOD, 1000) applied globally.
# wt >= 100 & INSTRUMENT_LOD >= 10 is an essential condition.
# wt >= 1,000 is a necessary condition for normal approximation validity.
# wi >= 1,000 is a necessary condition for Reliable_Taxa.
